{2940}{}{Attention! This is NCR Ranger commander Eliza speaking. The Republic's Rangers need your help. The approaches to the capital are occupied by gangs of raiders and slavers. We pay for every camp wiped out. Details from Sergeant Kyle. Over and out.}
{2941}{}{Attention! This is NCR Ranger commander Eliza speaking. On behalf of the NCR Army headquarters, I extend my gratitude to all who rendered aid. The raiders have been eliminated. I repeat. The raiders have been destroyed. Over and out.}
{2942}{}{This is one of the bandit camps threatening the security of the NCR.@@You have found one of the places where the raiders dug in before their decisive attack on the NCR.@@The most desperate cutthroats of the Wasteland have gathered here. They block the exits from the Republic's capital, kill patrolling rangers, and rob NCR caravans.}

