 #
 # Bulletin board in the NCR using in ncr_common.fos
 # ** BUYING ** 3100..3109
{3100}{}{URGENTLY buying Jet... and Buffout. Doctor Troy.}
{3101}{}{Will buy ammo for a solar scorcher at any price. The Chosen One}
{3102}{}{Will buy power armor, size 94 (Contact Marcus, sheriff of Broken Hills)}
{3103}{}{Will buy TVs, refrigerators, radios - GOOD MONEY. Vic}
{3104}{}{Will buy fertilizer, preferably the kind that doesn't cause dandruff. Harold}
{3105}{}{We'll buy an iron fly and iron men. The Wright children. Daddy will pay (probably). }
{3106}{}{Will buy contact lenses -3.5 for both eyes, will sell dental braces, used (apply at the Vault City Main Office, ask for the First Citizen)}
{3107}{}{We'll buy toilets!! The people of Modoc. Scratched in with a knife: Chosen, you bastard!!!}
{3108}{}{We'll buy a rubber doll of the Chosen One for testing new weapons. The ENCLAVE guards}
{3109}{}{Will buy garden pests. Sick of the plant humor! Typhon}
# ** LOOKING FOR ** 3110..3116
{3110}{}{Lost a robe, lilac with yellow stripes, please return for a reward. The Bridgekeeper.}
{3111}{}{Lost a doll=85 cm, with a yawning mouth, blonde... naked. Whoever finds it, please leave it by the building to the right at the entrance to Modoc.}
{3112}{}{Brahmin needed. Preferably the exploding kind. The Bridgekeeper.}
{3113}{}{We seek justice. The Rangers
We seek rangers. *Justice* [beneath the crossed-out text can be seen: "Slavers"]}
{3114}{}{Seeking young talent. Apply at the office in New Reno *Golden Globes Porn*}
{3115}{}{Looking for my eye. *Corporal Dixon*}
{3116}{}{Whoever finds a huge metal backside is earnestly requested not to laugh, not to show anyone, and to be sure to return it to "Enclave" LLC! F. Horrigan (upper part)}
# ** SELLING ** 3117..3130
{3117}{}{Selling oil, weapons, medicine, and we also have a GECK. The oil rig. Pickup only. Please do not blow up. Richardson}
{3118}{}{Selling Skynet, parts only is fine. Chosen One.}
{3119}{}{The first of July. 
Will buy energy cells to fuel my car. Payment negotiable. Chosen One.

The thirteenth of July. 
Selling loot. Including: grenades, pistols, machine guns, rifles, bazookas, melee weapons, armor, medicine, ammo (energy cells too). Cheap! (Had a good wander through the desert! Damn, where do I unload all this?) Chosen One.}
{3120}{}{Due to certain geopolitical changes, urgently selling a well-appointed oil rig with a working atomic reactor. President Richardson.}
{3121}{}{Toxic waste, self-pickup, at wholesale prices. Smiley.}
{3122}{}{Selling a base with all its contents and personnel. Price negotiable. Not for sale to Chosen Ones. Sergeant Granite.}
{3123}{}{Nuclear reactor for sale (used) with all amenities, stonework, premium renovation of 2143, price negotiable (RadAway and repair bot included). First Citizen of Vault City. Inquire from 8:00 to 18:00, must have a Day Pass on you.}
{3124}{}{Will buy a gauss vindicator, expensive, very expensive. (Contact Algernon, New Reno)}
{3125}{}{Selling a wanamingo gold mine in Redding. Wanamingos included. Sly McGrew.}
{3126}{}{Selling APA and a laser rifle. The Chosen One, Horrigan and the Tin Woodman are asked not to inquire! Sergeant Granite}
{3127}{}{- Selling a GECK, no longer needed. Chosen One
- Lord, what an idiot!!! <Elder>}
{3128}{}{Selling a gecko that sheds constantly. VERY expensive. Smiley.}
{3129}{}{Selling oil. President.}
{3130}{}{Selling scrap metal. Cheap. Self-pickup from Navarro.}
# ** РЕКЛАМА ** 3131..3138
{3131}{}{Liquor, wholesale and retail. The Wright Family.}
{3132}{}{Gecko-grill - a living grill-bar in your home. A wonderful device for quickly searing any dish. A rare natural variety of gecko. The best Christmas gift for your beloved mother-in-law. Warning - feed only while wearing a fireproof suit. Pet shop "Old Man Geckonych"}
{3133}{}{Free debates on the topic of who is the Chosen One. Talking Head.
  <scrawled below> "Stolen gems accepted at the Head" Chosen One.}
{3134}{}{We'll cure your drug addiction in 10 days. Myron.}
{3135}{}{Got money? THAT CAN BE FIXED! Raiders.}
{3136}{}{Express tanning, cheap, inquire at the Gecko power plant.}
{3137}{}{Collect five heads with a tattoo and get a ranger badge. NCR Rangers
